        "title": "GitHub-backed skill source sync",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nAdds GitHub-backed skill source support end to end:\n\n- source-backed Convex schema, sync planner, 15-minute cron, and verification state\n- install resolver that serves GitHub source metadata without mirroring install artifacts\n- OpenClaw/ClawHub CLI install/update support for GitHub-backed skills at verified commits\n- settings UI for configuring public GitHub skill sources\n- skill detail/profile rendering for cached GitHub `SKILL.md`, `skill-card.md`, and `skills.sh.json` grouping metadata\n\n## Security Notes\n\n- Scheduled sync revalidates that the upstream repo is still public before fetching source content.\n- Install/update uses the verified current GitHub commit and blocks stale or unverified upstream state.\n- GitHub zip extraction preserves verifier-accepted filenames such as `payload..sh` while still rejecting traversal path segments.\n- Source-backed install does not serve ClawHub-owned mirrored skill artifacts.\n\n## Verification Run So Far\n\nPassed:\n\n- `git diff --check`\n- `bunx vitest run convex/githubSkillSync.test.ts --reporter=dot`\n- `bun run --cwd packages/clawhub test:src src/cli/commands/skills.test.ts src/skills.test.ts`\n- `bunx oxfmt --check convex/githubSkillSync.ts convex/githubSkillSync.test.ts packages/clawhub/src/cli/commands/skills.ts packages/clawhub/src/cli/commands/skills.test.ts packages/clawhub/src/skills.ts packages/clawhub/src/skills.test.ts`\n- `bunx tsc --noEmit --pretty false`\n- earlier before final review-fix patch: `bun run ci:packages`, `bun run ci:unit`, `bun run ci:types-build`, `bun run ci:static`, `GITHUB_TOKEN=\"$(gh auth token)\" bun run ci:e2e-http`\n\nPaused before final closeout:\n\n- final `$autoreview` rerun after the last accepted fixes\n- final broad rerun of `ci:packages`, `ci:unit`, and `ci:types-build`\n\n## Follow-up Before Ready\n\n- Resume final autoreview and broad gate reruns.\n- Update/close the Linear child issues once verification is terminal.\n",
